# NIX PROFILE
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Manage user profiles (install/remove packages permanently).
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix profile install nixpkgs#htop: Install htop to the user profile.
- nix profile list: List all installed packages in the profile.

### Essentials
- nix profile remove htop: Uninstall a package by name or index.
- nix profile upgrade 0: Upgrade the package at index 0.

### Intermediaries
- nix profile history: Show the history of profile generations.
- nix profile rollback: Roll back to the previous generation.

### Advanceds
- nix profile wipe-history: Delete old profile generations.

## Tips
- Use 'nix profile list' to find the index number for removal/upgrade.

## Disclaimers
- Changes persist across reboots and shell sessions.

## Alternatives
- home-manager: Declarative profile management (highly recommended).

